branchCategory.description: <p>Vacuum Generator series 90-ZQ is designed for high speed break response handling applications.&nbsp; The 90-ZQ series can be used as a stand alone generator, or as part of a vacuum pump system. 90-ZQ is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing.</p>
